  <description type="morphology">Leaf blades 5–65 × 1–6(–12) mm, faces rough hairy to glabrate (hairs antrorse). Phyllaries usually lance-olate, lance-linear, or lance-elliptic, sometimes narrowly ovate, 0.9–7.5 × 0.5–2 mm, outer usually less than 1.6 mm wide, apices acute to blunt. Corollas 4.5–9 mm. Pappi 5–8 mm. 2n = 18.</description>
